{"tid":803040,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢係咪對我有意思?","createTime":"2018-09-02T02:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T03:16:50.000Z","uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2703bd3f445e7000fa6302d37ddece07b4860684","tid":803040,"uid":150912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:52:36.000Z","msg":"上夜校進修識左個女仔<br />\n一個星期見2次<br />\n原先約佢落堂食飯佢唔肯<br />\n之後大約3-4個月前佢終於肯同我食<br />\n每次上完堂都去食野,大家傾下計,<br />\n到最近2個星期<br />\n傾傾下瀲動時佢會捉住我隻手<br />\n然後依幾日都好大雨,落雨時佢冇帶遮<br />\n咁我有帶遮埋佢<br />\n佢挨埋黎撓住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁的行為<br />\n係咪對我有意思?<br />\n應否去馬?"},{"pid":"006f799bd69cbc59650de1829b9fe8a8d4109615","tid":803040,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"有可能，但唔係話一定要佢對你有意思先可以去馬"},{"pid":"2d4b01fc158e25e58c7ab2cf735e3c98ed0ab377","tid":803040,"uid":29879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:56:48.000Z","msg":"聽落似player<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd44eb8d5596a6bc54cd0414d63296d432243cce","tid":803040,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T02:58:33.000Z","msg":"唔代表d咩 有d女係特別多身體接觸"},{"pid":"9bb99c4b7052b32c01aaa1d924faf7f9bf5f85b2","tid":803040,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:10:41.000Z","msg":"可能有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261ab6eeda90e2c0b89a37924c823c8fb088e833","tid":803040,"uid":154986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:12:22.000Z","msg":"似收兵"},{"pid":"80c5475edd879b5fcc29f821ca3318a4033fba3f","tid":803040,"uid":12158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"係，已經好明顯"},{"pid":"c414aa15ed46c0b45b49e87f5fe8c590765637c0","tid":803040,"uid":199590,"like":2,"disli